Q26. How does the built-in <code>ngIf</code> structural directive change the rendered DOM based on this template syntax?
<p><code>ts
@Component({
  selector: 'app-product',
  template: '&lt;div *ngIf="product"&gt;{{ product.name }}&lt;/div&gt;',
})
export class ProductComponent {
  @Input() product;
}</code></p>

